  <official_title>A Multicenter, Double-Blind, Double-Dummy, Placebo-Controlled, Randomized, Parallel Group Evaluation of the Efficacy and Safety of a Fixed-Dose of Talnetant Versus Placebo Versus Risperidone in Subjects With Schizophrenia</official_title>
